data.description: This 1416 square foot single family home has 3 bedrooms and 2.0 bathrooms. Don't miss this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath CBS home with attached 2 car garage. Located in the desirable gated community of Emerald Lakes in south Stuart. LOW HOA fees includes lawn care, pool, tennis, and cable. Features a bright open floor plan with split bedrooms, Tall volume ceilings with 2 skylights. Corian counters. Tile in the living areas. 3 sliders lead to a relaxing screened patio. Master bedroom has 2 walk in closets. Very quiet neighborhood. Close to restaurants, shopping and the beaches. Move-in ready. No leasing for first year of ownership. price is firm. Based on the report several insurance companies have stated they will provide home insurance. Price is based accordingly. Home is sold "as is" and the price is firm.
